    "body": "@RafaelAPB - you're right, the private equivalent of https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.2.0/web3-eth-contract.html hasn't been implemented yet.  You can use [priv_call](https://besu.hyperledger.org/en/stable/Reference/API-Methods/#priv_call) to access private state.  It can also be invoked from the [web3js-eea library](https://pegasyseng.github.io/web3js-eea/latest/EEAClient.html#~call). ",
